      限定符和类型 类和说明
      class  AggregationIterator
      Iterator that aggregates multiple spans or time series data and does linear interpolation (lerp) for missing data points.
      class  Downsampler
      Iterator that downsamples data points using an Aggregator.
      class  FillingDownsampler
      A specialized downsampler that returns special values, based on the fill policy, for intervals for which no data could be found.
      class  MutableDataPoint
      A mutable DataPoint that stores a value and a timestamp.
